{"h4b005286g8850g4fa3ga0bcgff5754d6cd1d": ["How about some rest? It's been quite an evening.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c51b6d96-60b7-26d4-d4e4-b1b77aa8407c"], "h8b71af61gdc86g4430g8c3fgfd017bc3f1e5": ["Don't you love the silence after a massacre? It's just so pure.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "001e00c0-f01f-8dde-51c7-b21c6bf2c856"], "hb9c8341bg2e06g4243ga615gb367c96816cf": ["Certainly better than pillow talk with your drow lover, hmm?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "4c8d832d-d007-37df-eef8-96b924494bc2"], "h137d4d86g121ag422agb1a2gf7030d376187": ["Not quite yet, love. Let's wait until they're asleep.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "926d9c53-568c-f34d-5fb1-c5dd6646f483"], "heb9cc7acgb391g4eebg9ebagd50f99b731f6": ["If you're here to beg forgiveness, save your breath. My cup and I are perfectly happy together.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "10db5e17-127f-b54d-d6b8-4589ec452615"], "hba697457ge21ag4598g9180gbea77adc5481": ["Oh don't come crawling back. It's just embarrassing.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c948d169-803b-e90c-3a7a-78cbd28f3b85"], "h246e33c7g2b53g42cdg97e0g2e3951113b48": ["Well hello. Welcome to my humble party.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "26b3bd36-db1a-d353-e529-69b7ac265f51"], "h7b3dbc0fgab20g48abg8be9g7853eb8bc731": ["What's your poison? Red? White?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "efb09ea4-5e60-d635-8fb6-76b6e4ac0cc5"], "hba1caf86g103cg4054gac8dgce82a4e53812": ["White.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "4cfe1a88-8e75-f483-8d93-c88098ee6c8e"], "hb9afa847g82f4g40dfg94begc9d792be4361": ["I'm afraid it's warm, but needs must.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "2c39551c-82be-ec43-f7f2-1d157496424b"], "hcebddfbegfb37g435fgae2ag059555db2f56": ["So, what are we drinking to? Other than a pile of corpses.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "1bdd7cd4-ce08-7bd5-787d-6003653cf563"], "h8668c465g5a9cg4d91ga688gb00e55f041d7": ["To victory, of course.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "2c73d397-e7a1-dc1c-807e-8c0b9a10703f"], "hd56d1761gf72bg4862g9953g5ced6fe1ce32": ["To victory!", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "8498ebd6-e5da-5e75-b6bb-9259125651aa"], "h05647596g9c02g4c9dg96a5g419d5c1c9fe6": ["To surviving another day.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "93b90fff-4b9b-7b91-62c1-c84a167284da"], "h96429ca7gf43ag4e85g8772g563f3605013c": ["To surviving!", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "1401c07a-66f2-ba61-eb47-a8ddc3c22ef0"], "h6b178bb9g5a79g4b21gabf1gb25523b4789b": ["To getting rid of this tadpole.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "a941011e-2c8e-e1aa-a24a-fc771a01250f"], "hd38ff5d9gd10bg4d72g8784gbc2f90580075": ["Cheers.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "f4748b76-6e61-51c3-18cc-24f0563d77cc"], "h77dc33b2gdf35g469cg8bc4g5e9eff649d52": ["That's not funny.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "17fa39d6-490c-0790-8a0a-4a478fa0be9c"], "h4cf67e6bg5cfdg49d4g9412g06df8740c2ef": ["Oh don't be so sour - it's a party.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "5943c6f5-505a-9c64-48e1-db5a2d41ac08"], "h260ff2beg567fg48b2g849fg826df0b272b8": ["You did what you had to. Don't be ashamed that you did it well.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c12fd69c-36a5-1ec6-ff1f-41185bb0ba6a"], "h838bc0ebg9820g401cga154gc81e58a2103e": ["I wish things had turned out differently.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "0c6d3fe1-53ea-e8df-e27f-d6cf05637059"], "h12a8d0e5gf557g4498g805cg4f573a9160db": ["And I wish I was drinking out of the skulls of everyone who's ever wronged me. Life is tough.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "26b35883-7a04-7a5c-3af4-fc4c15d81304"], "hdd675a01g75dcg46a9g9710g494bd89e7e79": ["Although that's not to say we can't have a little fun.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "5bbcb6ce-5f7d-6965-7c88-153dbd93d990"], "hdf0412cdgb157g4128g996cg501082f9d6fc": ["Mmm. Delicious.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "f335ef57-5f25-5780-5daf-491f5c605fc3"], "h09a1954dg083ag49c9g9e1dg7e2dad1afef9": ["So, I see Lae'zel's marked you as her territory.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "0817c2fe-f0f8-d8b1-d969-e75891cc2c17"], "h9b597db2ge093g4a7egb9adg8962d5f2f13a": ["I just hope she leaves you in one piece. We can't take a week for you to recover from whatever her idea of 'fun' is.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "7f59a5f1-fccc-5960-46a9-fee4e85e3bc6"], "hbcc3e31dg711cg498cgbff9g659cf2ba3fad": ["I'm sure I'll have a good time.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "a060d0ac-c1ec-c8f0-e3d4-276a8a9f8e1d"], "h0a1fccd3gb7aag4ce6g9cfbgd39602afe6a9": ["Good for you. As for me, I'm going to drink until I'm sure I won't hear you grunting in the bushes.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "ee76b08e-5886-424d-1232-095bc728558c"], "h9d750052gcca6g4d23gbd1fga63c54a273e6": ["Here's to you!", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "bcc94818-e8ca-c7a8-2a4d-1769b395c6e7"], "hb719c363g4355g4f4bgbc78g437b5ee7aebb": ["It's nothing serious.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "07ec4ac9-4fd4-febf-15b7-61239cd555ae"], "h05ea31d0ge45fg415fgb982g5a3ebf4d0e5c": ["Ha! No, it so rarely is. But it might be fun.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "aa17b90b-ebc7-8f05-f0d9-c76c0c3c5c2f"], "h77e9653bg91f8g4fedgb776g1a76bca3afb1": ["You're not jealous, are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "05acbe87-a0dd-b4b5-406a-09cfca16bf67"], "h875954bcgc4ccg45b6g857eg7eae4d42c4b7": ["Ha! No, my love, I'm not jealous of the beating our gith friend will give you.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "163b87c4-bdb0-95dd-fb51-7ce8ac989815"], "h95b52433ge41dg4bb3g8184g27449bf1883b": ["As for me, I'm going to drink until I know I won't hear you grunting in the bushes.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "18fb6868-d742-f259-2ce4-e3d1db6c2b86"], "h0b5e896ag037dg4b8bgb6f6ge1e49cad69be": ["Ha! No, my love, you and Shadowheart can hold hands all you want. It means nothing to me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "64ca604e-0d45-8969-caf9-d5d6e00d48f5"], "h3198fb3eg8d98g4605g8e34gd88c10436771": ["Ha! No, my love, I'm not jealous of the drow. You have all the fun you want - if you survive the night.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "a3a7f73b-0fbc-7e6d-9101-8f3997913d5c"], "hacfe7c63g27ecg436cga21eg0c4c8304a256": ["So, I see you and Shadowheart have a connection. It looks very sweet.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "03e1f87d-f8cc-0053-b2ae-45121758c1c8"], "h27edc726g5ddbg41c6g84fbgb57f2ba2c272": ["Not what I'd call 'fun', or 'interesting', but sweet.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "42eff682-1695-e9e7-cd76-a8377c237aab"], "hc76c9681g4b0dg4cadgba5dg93ae32366555": ["So, I see you and the drow have been making eyes at each other.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "332bf097-b200-f7c9-071a-f84b2e5f082c"], "h0390cce8gdbfbg41bcg9b09g41fce7bfe683": ["She does seem like a fun romp. As long as she doesn't bite your head off halfway through the act.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "ee99a33d-b34a-0417-9d14-618e987bc880"], "h8f18c007gbbc5g4ba5g9a00gc84e4974b050": ["Are you offering anything better? Because I could be persuaded...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "4fc45306-a808-3c77-8224-7bcd668de810"], "h83793336gecafg44e1gaefdgd6a0e762323c": ["So, has anyone in the camp caught your eye?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "805c49e3-d2ee-e1fa-8488-5344ab7a3426"], "h2196632bga754g49c2gb362g45bc1d1ce23b": ["What do you mean?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c389c4c1-0832-69a6-9a2e-a60d32bf8606"], "h933c6728ga644g4185g8cbeg55d5cc34a27b": ["By the Hells. Sex, my dear. A night of passion.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c9c8cc99-5f47-31f3-8560-d49a3dc29466"], "h6fd67c4eg1c94g482ag80f8ge01aa0a07ac5": ["There's no better way to unwind after a long day of killing.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "4564a677-940e-02cd-bd28-e37829ce03a2"], "h69cbab3bgef1eg4c44g9c9cg62f1d9680ca6": ["Shadowheart is looking very good tonight...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "e6edd559-4a69-b429-0b52-d91680621aca"], "he7bbb384g1153g4517gba86g6561d8b43eea": ["Really? Her? ", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "6f700de6-f4d9-72ab-95fa-8d4c1b734422"], "hcc0f989ag687dg4bf1ga675gb078b1d9f5a5": ["Whatever makes you happy, I suppose. As long as you don't come scratching at my door.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "f4f9f5d0-e29f-e77c-e32e-3102d83be353"], "h86245402g0327g47bdg859eg14fdced3fec6": ["I bet Minthara is fun.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "a1a52e09-aa23-2f33-6472-2ea3b5787bf2"], "h47ca8468ge2d3g4cfbg8940gf14b7eb16bac": ["I'm sure she is. If you can trust her not to bite your head off once you've done the deed.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "cc7841ac-cf8e-8d37-29f0-a6467ad834ff"], "hb25cfa78gb6ceg4c9agaaf7gf4cb87077706": ["I'm tempted by Lae'zel.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "971bf696-96e6-940b-19c4-db20f5ca60fb"], "he25f19cdgfc71g4931g9060g2b4ebe361829": ["Ha! You're braver than I thought.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "5b19fe50-21cd-6fad-14b7-64a312623da8"], "h2ba25fb1ge6e8g43d8g8c0eg7d49c189321d": ["I was thinking about you, actually.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "fd9cb160-481f-65f8-068c-6f16d707794a"], "ha57fee49gfd0ag4992gac4egf9906887f1bf": ["No, I'll spend the night alone.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "0876960b-3a05-89b2-9711-0191797633ae"], "h34d8bedfgab6eg4831gaaa7g0eea9c64a769": ["So. What happens next?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "ac8675bb-fcc6-d8bb-de40-b351500ac519"], "hbdc8484fgf4bag475fg8849g051d48cd78a1": ["What do you mean?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "1d804c98-ac3d-cb9d-8cee-c43470b46442"], "h99fc1454g75dag4220gb88dg527ae6029139": ["What would you like to happen?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "422937fd-b93c-665f-9613-e0d18963c717"], "ha44079bfgc311g4a00ga42dgdda2f3e29fee": ["Oh, a little talking, a little drinking, and - once everyone else is asleep - we get to know each other.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "bdcc3e8d-74e5-cee3-2478-c04be5eacceb"], "he8986f3dg8c25g41d7gae61gb20f3b88762b": ["Well, I'd planned to bed you...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "7d37417b-29c7-ba1d-215a-cbdf6795d9ed"], "hd9eb6163g4e42g4b81g9914g59d6878f3f7a": ["Does Lae'zel know that? I saw how she looked at you earlier.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "07fa2d87-7b75-85af-b5e4-c9f02b160fec"], "h9f521f5ag1f34g4fbfgb384gff84a8379c0e": ["I'd hate to get between the gith and her trophy. No, I think we'll end this evening as friends.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "d65275e7-0b8e-ed93-1ddf-09b27fab0eae"], "h221bbb9fge315g4a19gb518g3a7e37636263": ["Does Shadowheart know that? I saw how she looked at you earlier.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "a71f2279-bbc7-cc83-f156-aa624f83aaa7"], "h5cdbe298gf86fg44acga84cg37498882ce65": ["I don't know what her idea of a good time is, but it seems to involve you. I'd hate to intrude.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "219e0dbd-0c34-7231-3f8d-14d889c6efdf"], "hbe56ed93g5ce9g4399g9b9dga43edcbf3f1c": ["Does the drow know that? I saw how she looked at you earlier.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "7a5f2fd6-bbb1-5af9-dbb2-1a680bbbd7e9"], "hb0337b76g09dfg438cg8a80g9aa98e39cdd2": ["Be careful with that one. Her idea of a good time probably involves biting your head off halfway through the act.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "7ca349e5-2219-f523-9ce4-9f2d3b890f62"], "h53123b6dg81b8g4eb2g8afdg5bd9fd62168f": ["Although I'm sure you'd know better than I would.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "301e5389-5ceb-f0ff-3ff2-2365a1bdb36f"], "h78cfa5a0g5553g4c36gac50g941114fc9081": ["Really? I thought you had other company planned this evening, and I'd hate to intrude.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "0766085c-0ee3-e808-2793-1ca2ea1f9a0d"], "h5d6b133fg219ag4617g99bfg775cc75af5bd": ["Watch maybe, but not intrude.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "61714039-4437-4d7b-25f7-fc01a9cb5a1e"], "h8380897egc570g4943g818ag5a54d3124938": ["Well, I'd hate to get in the way of a well-laid plan. So to speak.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "3b219842-dcb8-cf9b-f68c-cd8a4e1b38e5"], "hf0fa1251g962dg4b16g8095g2937bf5d52d0": ["Let's wait until things quieten down a bit. Once the others are asleep, we'll find each other. ", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "0a540413-9708-da1e-de61-c3996fde396b"], "h96ed6f39g90dcg482egbb83gc56c12884075": ["I'll see you later, then.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "6d1df08f-7d9f-f82a-cf6d-b9c8c1248071"], "h408bcb34g6036g457dg8e29g30eeec191920": ["Indeed you will, my love. Indeed you will.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "4a00d0c0-3977-a223-1fbc-2362415a95b4"], "h1cc630e5gcb01g439bgb24cgaf460a09c725": ["On second thought, maybe we'd better not.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c2c43b9b-fc0e-0b38-e4a0-9fa19576088b"], "h6efc7205gce87g4e82g9875g5208628c6459": ["Never listen to your second thoughts! They always spoil the fun.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "07985b7e-c342-e64d-2c81-0a7b9843134b"], "h6c18fb82gcb84g4f5eg95eage58c8ee60b39": ["But fine. If you're determined to ruin your evening, I won't stop you.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "3b2b0734-cec2-236c-521c-1995c04e61b7"], "h8a4ef9d4g74c0g4c0cg92f5g24523072e2dc": ["I'm flattered, but I think not. It's not you, you understand, it's me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "8d069579-9fe1-8782-79c2-e51d7dd2d3d6"], "h2af13822g88d6g49d8g843dgc62f62500f1f": ["I have standards.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "4acc5f9f-9ee4-4067-d39d-4922af8c9761"], "h594083c0g60a0g4160g9e6cg7c7dd7203791": ["Between us? Nothing.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "d65810a3-49f5-4269-e9b7-7aa982ea23f6"], "h7a595ba7g3f13g4cc0g8dc5ge41c78d6352d": ["Nothing? How can you be so cruel?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "da3d6aa3-e3b0-ea5c-fe7d-71b6933074f8"], "ha5f2dd59g823dg413cgbc16gff0f7d8b0b1b": ["Come on. There's a spark here. I know you've felt it too, darling.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "76d10d9f-fe07-ea51-aced-65c73aeadf0a"], "h0febb04dg72ddg4505ga0efg2d04c9da8036": ["I'd rather bed one of the goblins, <i>darling</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "4b686f31-2070-bd39-31d1-5418fdac3967"], "had6a4a59g1fceg442cg9397g891480227635": ["You are an insolent little pup, aren't you?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "f57378d1-b120-f1c1-d917-54c375e84b34"], "h4bd79260g31fag41f8g8618g6490d285887e": ["But have it your way. I'm happy to entertain myself.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "b1d53c35-72cd-6b36-e387-05a4e9b857b0"], "h749820a7ga6b2g44d2g9acdg0db91aeecb65": ["There isn't. I haven't. And that's all there is to it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "795470b3-c0fb-ded0-3fa5-56dc1b68c465"], "heae61d2bgec0ag4664gb45cgd50ed6778329": ["I'm sorry, I mistook you for someone with taste.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "52ad4a7e-bbcb-f9b9-29df-bbbbf1799487"], "hfeae1f96ge63bg4a5bga45bgee78d4f59f2c": ["Maybe. If you say 'please.'", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "0be944a7-3140-a69d-54e3-dff27d5efe3a"], "h905ee7b4g86deg461bga271gc14141de14a6": ["What?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "94b759bd-1b93-89a5-bb0e-a3096c156cb5"], "hea56db99ga6b7g4fbeg820fgee1e454398f5": ["Say 'please'.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "164cab5a-c331-ecac-4efd-1490fc0d041e"], "h0e8c8576g753fg4c2cg96e8g024104dd2af8": ["<i>Please.</i>", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "ce4dea2f-99fe-b54f-bf26-b8093828bfd3"], "h94485213g2b60g4fa6gab2bge23e054d2778": ["No.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "1c823bd2-1c37-ff7f-5795-a62e6547e1cb"], "head5d4b0g105ag492cga683gb3e5f4145b2e": ["You insolent little-", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "642e1395-1557-f50d-2421-6445e63a0cfb"], "h771e8273gad38g4685gb373g674a956c8850": ["Fine. Enjoy your night with whatever goblin will have you.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "de18b720-c3df-993d-2a65-a3a1143628ba"], "hf71bd800g54d8g4690gbb43g998b73dec493": ["Well done! I'll see you tonight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "8bcbba53-78a0-27bf-f991-c428cbb83efe"], "h57c02544g809ag46b1gb0dcgfe5e4151e14d": ["Cheeky little pup. I'll see you later.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "e14ec68a-98ee-db69-03d7-d0cfb7ce744b"], "hcae7d04eg4a47g4e50g98dbg43f1372502a3": ["I'm kidding. I'll see you tonight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "82275048-ccc3-ebf8-10ae-0595bf2d2ec7"], "h9c0265f5g3268g4806gb8c6geac2534c0344": ["Cheeky little pup. I'll see you later.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "7a7c1285-3ee9-b98a-e897-ac0247ffc46b"], "h05d484e7gc78dg4d3cg9c56g33457a505fb4": ["No, Astarion. It's not happening.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "d2ca65a7-7d25-f31b-902d-c26d8a136514"], "ha3387cb2g184dg4a04g8c23g682a91a18674": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "07646367-3805-63b9-0fe9-b4105687b16a"], "h2a47a274ga0bag4bb9gbe2cg63b0174955f7": ["Suit yourself. I've more than enough company.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "3ab7dd0f-36cb-606b-f05f-8f301192fa8e"], "h8560fc2egd638g435bga9ccg3d1db2288e71": ["And I wish I was drinking out of Cazador's skull. Life is tough.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "98dce0e8-5184-8196-5393-57a483ed4f3b"], "h255c618dg6435g4677g817fg2bd7b9457abe": ["I'm not ashamed. I just don't feel like boasting about it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "9754de82-5773-5663-42f2-5fc7239a2100"], "h9e679e27g9df4g4690ga520g2e038b42f497": ["Try it. You might have fun.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntRaiderCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "1f3ef1b7-12aa-1d7d-d310-15b4d547c8c5"], "ha5280a6cg2b82g400fga0adg5386bf0714fe": ["To fun!", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dia